<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: Confused about the resolution]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=4815&amp;p=42671#p42671"><![CDATA[
The vertical resolution of the NES is 240 scanlines, not 224. Don't be fooled by emulators that crop the top and bottom 8 scanlines. And yes, the total is 262: 20 are VBlank, 1 is pre-render, 240 are rendered and 1 is a dummy.<br /><br />If this doc says the resolution is 256x224, you should stop reading it right now. Who knows what else could be wrong?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=95">tokumaru</a> — Sun Feb 01, 2009 8:16 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
